WEBVTT

00:06.351 --> 00:08.177
What's your favorite season?

00:08.777 --> 00:11.220
My favorite season is spring.

00:11.928 --> 00:14.195
The weather is cool and sunny.

00:14.699 --> 00:16.650
I like to plant flowers.

00:17.265 --> 00:19.107
Wow, that's really great.

00:19.755 --> 00:21.217
How about you, Arthur?

00:21.889 --> 00:23.499
What's your favorite season?

00:23.969 --> 00:26.859
My favorite season is summer.

00:27.491 --> 00:33.476
I like hot weather because I can go to the beach and sunbathe.

00:34.299 --> 00:38.055
I love having cold drinks on the beach.

00:38.671 --> 00:40.010
That sounds good too.

00:40.968 --> 00:42.597
How about you, Sandra?

00:43.462 --> 00:45.071
What's your favorite season?

00:45.935 --> 00:47.675
My favorite season is autumn.

00:48.510 --> 00:49.917
I love to go hiking.

00:50.755 --> 00:52.447
All the leaves are changing color.

00:53.281 --> 00:55.047
The trees look so beautiful.

00:55.891 --> 00:57.003
How about you, Luke?

00:57.841 --> 00:59.194
What's your favorite season?

01:00.190 --> 01:02.061
My favorite season is winter.

01:02.895 --> 01:04.879
Summer is too hot for me.

01:05.909 --> 01:09.093
I like cold weather and love to go snowboarding.

01:10.116 --> 01:12.347
So winter is best for me.

